_sText:
This Map is for 32 Player max!

Nearly everything that looks like a ladder, is a ladder (exept for some cables).

And don't be afraid of jumping on softly objects.

There is a lot of interaction possible in the Map, search for it. ;)

Note: sadly there is no light you can manipulate because of the engine.

All custom content is self-made.

You can play it here:

78.46.89.24:27015

or download it from www.mappingbase.de

http://download.gc-gaming.de/bashor/mappingbase/css_maps/deratsbrb_final.rar
